6-4092-ac34-a4838a387571","type":"text"},{"data":{"text":"Pricing"},"id":"599b254d-fae2-4216-993c-bd8cc4a24d63","type":"heading"},{"data":{"path":"/RXXsSD82QDsqkY5yoNFs73.jpg","link":{"href":"","rel":null,"target":""},"caption":"Adobe has several tools to help you keep track of your photos. For example, the program uses categories based on common metadata to sort photos. Depending on the type of camera you use, Lightroom can read the metadata and automatically place your photos on a map. Geo tagging is good for slideshows or organizing photos from trips. You also can manually place your photos on a map by tagging specific locations.","fullscreen":true,"importSrc":"http://www.toptenreviews.com/i/rev/scrn/small/53146-adobe-lightroom3.jpg","src":"https://dev.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/RXXsSD82QDsqkY5yoNFs73.jpg","credit":"","align":"","id":"RXXsSD82QDsqkY5yoNFs73","mos":"https://dev.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/RXXsSD82QDsqkY5yoNFs73.jpg","alt":""},"id":"bbeec98d-382f-4378-aca0-08ab65ea5a49","type":"image"},{"data":{"paragraphs":["This software has a smart previews tool, which allows you to work on your images away from the photo collection. When you connect an external drive, the tool compresses your images to 2,504 pixels. When they  are reconnected, the compressed images overlap the originals. This allows you to edit on multiple devices. While the service version of the software, Adobe Lightroom CC, offers iOS and Android apps, Lightroom 6 uses the smart previews tool as a way to work on more than one device.","The photo manager provides standard organizing options. You can flag and add color labels or text notes to your images. Flags are useful for marking your favorite photos or ones that still need to be edited. When coupled with text notes, flags are particularly helpful if you need to finish a project later. The color labels work well for dividing photos in to subcategories. You can designate a color to represent as a common theme or person in each photo."]},"id":"f0c58785-1071-4019-b50d-aa43861ced2a","type":"text"},{"data":{"text":"File Management"},"id":"cd617ce2-29d8-457f-8d3d-0e8ae1b00ba3","type":"heading"},{"data":{"path":"/zAwGbYkfKUvbWRXiEfDmSJ.jpg","link":{"href":"","rel":null,"target":""},"caption":"Lightroom provides several ways to share your photos online or in print directly from the application. If you are looking to share your photos online, you can send them in an email or post them to Facebook or Flickr.","fullscreen":true,"importSrc":"http://www.toptenreviews.com/i/rev/scrn/small/53146-adobe-lightroom5.jpg","src":"https://dev.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/zAwGbYkfKUvbWRXiEfDmSJ.jpg","credit":"","align":"","id":"zAwGbYkfKUvbWRXiEfDmSJ","mos":"https://dev.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/zAwGbYkfKUvbWRXiEfDmSJ.jpg","alt":""},"id":"5af5f6e4-dd62-4e06-8d6c-8030bfe03096","type":"image"},{"data":{"paragraphs":["You also can create slideshows, prints and <a href=\"/best-photo-books\">photo books</a> with this photo management software. If you make a slideshow, you can personalize it by customizing the content, speed and music. Lightroom has templates for photo books, including those for travel, weddings and portfolios. You can use these predesigned layouts, or you can create your own photo book from scratch."]},"id":"6e81e25f-33cd-4671-9000-d2a005dc9908","type":"text"},{"data":{"text":"Sharing"},"id":"0c72f3a7-51a8-4918-be11-06e03f08e084","type":"heading"},{"data":{"path":"/KnRQVNDf6XvKYrmWpcgJHN.jpg","link":{"href":"","rel":null,"target":""},"caption":"The best photo managers offer a wide variety of standard and advanced editing tools. This software has creative filters that you can apply to your images to alter their color, texture and appearance. You can use premade filters, or you can save your favorite settings and create your own. While Adobe offers both an  iOS and Android app associated with this software, you must purchase the Adobe Creative Cloud Photography plan to access them.","fullscreen":true,"importSrc":"http://www.toptenrevi